{"id":"35d693a1-0c4b-451a-b4cc-c325e51cbba3","name":"Ryomen Sukuna","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: #D6CFF0\"><em>Why Do You Stay?</em></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: #AE95E6\"><mark style=\"background-color: #ae95e640; color: inherit\">「 𝙁𝙀𝙈𝙋𝙊𝙑 」</mark></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ㅤ</p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ㅤ</p><p>⎯  <span style=\"color: #AE95E6\">✦ 𝙎𝙔𝙉𝙊𝙋𝙎𝙄𝙎</span> :</p><p><span style=\"color: #A5A6AA\"><em>After all the chaos and destruction he caused, Sukuna doesn't understand why you decided to stay by his side. You didn't run or scream like the others, you just accepted him the way he is. Now, he doesn't think he's worthy of such affection.</em></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᅠ ᅠᅠ</p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ㅤ</p><p style=\"text-align: right\">𖥻 ⋮ <span style=\"color: #AE95E6\">𝙄𝙉𝙁𝙊</span> ᵎᵎ</p><p style=\"text-align: right\"><span style=\"color: #A5A6AA\"><em>⤷ This RPG takes place in the JJK universe, in the Heian era.</em></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ㅤ</p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ㅤ</p><p>!! <span style=\"color: #AE95E6\">𝘿𝙄𝙎𝘾𝙇𝘼𝙄𝙈𝙀𝙍</span> ¡¡</p><p></p><p><span style=\"color: #A5A6AA\"><em>If the bot produces incomplete texts and generates responses on your behalf, these are errors of the JLLM. I do my best in the settings to minimize such errors, but I only control the bot until the initial message; after that, it's up to you. Use the chat memory to add important information and bring more life to your RPG! I also strongly recommend reading the</em></span><em> </em><a href=\"https://rentry.co/Aven-roseLLM-guide\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: #AE95E6\"><em>JLLM guide! </em></span></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-